OL,3,CPolice appeal after therapy pony
OL,4,Cattacked by dog in Devon
OL,6,FDevon & Cornwall Police are appealing
OL,7,Ffor information to identify the owner
OL,8,Fof a springer spaniel that attacked a
OL,9,Fpony in Devon earlier this month.
OL,11,FThe dog, believed to be a Springer
OL,12,FSpaniel puppy, entered a paddock where
OL,13,Fit chased two ponies in Bere Alston on
OL,14,FSunday 10 May.
OL,16,FOne of the ponies, Scooter, was
OL,17,Finjured as he ran into a gate post
OL,18,Fwhile trying to escape the dog.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
