PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779444433
OL,3,CPolice appeal after therapy pony
OL,4,Cattacked by dog in Devon
OL,6,FThe owner of the dog is described as
OL,7,Fbeing female, between 20 and 30, and
OL,8,Froughly 5ft 6ins tall. She was also
OL,9,Fdescribed as "well-spoken" and had
OL,10,Fdark hair which was pulled back into a
OL,11,Fponytail.
OL,13,FThe dog is described as being a six-
OL,14,Fmonth-old brown and white Springer
OL,15,FSpaniel. It was also wearing a harness
OL,16,Fat the time of the incident.
OL,18,FScooter is part of Collytown Therapy
OL,19,FPonies, which provides support to
OL,20,Fneurodivergent children in the local
OL,21,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
