PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779444433
OL,3,CPolice appeal after therapy pony
OL,4,Cattacked by dog in Devon
OL,6,FCharmaine Blamey is Scooter's owner,
OL,7,Fand runs Collytown Therapy Ponies.
OL,9,F"Scooter is part of our family and a
OL,10,Fcompanion to our other horses. He is
OL,11,Falso part of 'Collytown Therapy
OL,12,FPonies' - a service we provide to
OL,13,Fsupport neurodivergent children in our
OL,14,Flocal community.
OL,16,F"I would like the owner to come
OL,17,Fforward; to see the damage her dog has
OL,18,Fcaused, and to have a valuable
OL,19,Fconversation about how this kind of
OL,20,Fincident can be prevented in the
OL,21,Ffuture.
OL,26,@qD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
