PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779444433
OL,3,CPolice appeal after therapy pony
OL,4,Cattacked by dog in Devon
OL,6,F"If you're not sure of your dog's
OL,7,Frecall ability, please, please, please
OL,8,Fput your dog on a lead around other
OL,9,Fanimals."
OL,11,FPC Lucy Wyatt, lead for Equine Crime
OL,12,Fat Devon & Cornwall Police said: "This
OL,13,Fis a very distressing incident which
OL,14,Fhighlights the risk to animals,
OL,15,Fincluding livestock, when dogs are not
OL,16,Funder proper control.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
