PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779444433
OL,3,CPolice appeal after therapy pony
OL,4,Cattacked by dog in Devon
OL,6,F"We are urging anyone who has
OL,7,Finformation about this incident, or
OL,8,Fwho may be able to identify the owner
OL,9,For the dog involved based on the
OL,10,Fdescription provided, to please come
OL,11,Fforward.
OL,13,F"If you are the owner of the dog
OL,14,Finvolved, please do the right thing
OL,15,Fand make contact with us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
